*idjc-0.8.3 (11 Aug 2010)

  11 Aug 2010; Gavin Pryke <gavinlee303@googlemail.com> -idjc-0.6.10.ebuild,
  -idjc-0.6.11_pre1.ebuild, -idjc-0.6.11.ebuild, -idjc-0.6.12.ebuild,
  -idjc-0.7.0.ebuild, -idjc-0.7.2a.ebuild, +idjc-0.8.3.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  remove ebuilds with non-existant SRC_URI, move HOMEPAGE and SRC_URI to
  sourceforge based site. add wma USE flag to metadata. bump to 0.8.3.

